    <section id="full-body">
        <h2>1. Full Body Workouts</h2>
        <ul>
            <li>
                <strong>10 Push-ups</strong> – Perform 10 to 15 push-ups per set, 3 sets.  
                <a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=_l3ySVKYVJ8" target="_blank">Watch Tutorial</a>
            </li>
            <li>
                <strong>10 Dumbbell Squats</strong> – Hold the dumbbell and perform 10–12 reps, 3 sets.  
                <a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=1sJEt21vmWA" target="_blank">Watch Tutorial</a>
            </li>
            <li>
                <strong>10 Dumbbell Deadlifts</strong> – Do 10–12 reps, 3 sets.  
                <a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=gC2yhtJ2cY4" target="_blank">Watch Tutorial</a>
            </li>
        </ul>
    </section>

    <section id="abs">
        <h2>2. Adding Ab Exercises</h2>
        <ul>
            <li>
                <strong>Russian Twists</strong> – 10 to 12 twists per side, 3 sets.  
                <a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=wkD8rjkodUI" target="_blank">Watch Tutorial</a>
            </li>
            <li>
                <strong>Leg Raises</strong> – 10 to 15 reps, 3 sets.  
                <a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=JB2oyawG9KI" target="_blank">Watch Tutorial</a>
            </li>
            <li>
                <strong>Plank</strong> – Hold for 20 to 30 seconds, 3 sets.  
                <a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ASdvN_XEl_c" target="_blank">Watch Tutorial</a>
            </li>
        </ul>
    </section>

    <section id="upper-body">
        <h2>3. Upper Body Focused Workouts</h2>
        <ul>
            <li>
                <strong>Dumbbell Shoulder Press</strong> – 10 to 12 reps, 3 sets.  
                <a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=B-aVuyhvLHU" target="_blank">Watch Tutorial</a>
            </li>
            <li>
                <strong>Dumbbell Rows</strong> – 10 to 12 reps per arm, 3 sets.  
                <a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=roCP6wCXPqo" target="_blank">Watch Tutorial</a>
            </li>
            <li>
                <strong>Bicep Curls</strong> – 10 to 12 reps per arm, 3 sets.  
                <a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=in7PaeYlhrM" target="_blank">Watch Tutorial</a>
            </li>
        </ul>
